&lt;p&gt;Are you newly qualified Nurse looking to start your career in a supportive, innovative and fast pacing environment? Or you may be an experienced Nurse looking to develop your skills and knowledge in surgical Nursing. If you answered yes then come and join our well established friendly and supportive team here on 7 North, Ealing Hospital Site. Our team is dynamic, forward thinking and constantly striving to improve the patient’s pathway, with an emphasis on patient experience, high quality patient centered care and team working.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We can offer you:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;-Newly qualified Nurses are enrolled onto our Trusts preceptorship programme.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;-On-going learning and development including access to mentorship and leadership courses.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;-Clearly structured career pathway and personal development plan -On-going support from our enthusiastic and innovative team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you are a highly motivated team player with a keen interest in surgical Nursing, then we would be really pleased to hear from you.&lt;/p&gt;
